name: Mackenzie Floating Rate Income ETF
longDescription: The ETF seeks to generate current income. In order to achieve its investment objective, Mackenzie Floating Rate Income ETF invests primarily in floating rate debt instruments and/or high yield debt securities of issuers located anywhere in the world. Mackenzie Floating Rate Income ETF invests primarily in floating rate instruments, such as senior loans and floating rate notes.
fulldescription: The ETF seeks to generate current income. It may also invest in fixed rate high yield corporate bonds or other debt obligations
